title: Now Yearbook 1986 / Various - Limited
description: Limited hard back book packaging. Four CD set. NOW Music is proud to present the next instalment of the 'Yearbook' series, NOW - Yearbook 1986, featuring 80 tracks from a fantastic year in pop! Includes tracks from George Michael, A-ha, Duran Duran, Kate Bush, Eurythmics, Falco, Level 42, Kim Wilde, Nick Kamen, Owen Paul, The Bangles, the Pretenders, Paul Simon, UB40, Simply Red, Spandau Ballet, the Communards, Bananarama, Debbie Harry, Belouis Some, The Blow Monkeys, Swing Out Sister, Aretha Franklin, Gwen Guthrie, Cameo, Jermaine Stewart, Whitney Houston, Lionel Richie, The Smiths, Frankie Goes To Hollywood, Sigue Sigue Sputnick, New Order, Furniture, Public Image Limited, It's Immaterial, Big Audio Dynamite, Talk Talk, Simple Minds, The Psychedelic Furs, Berlin, The Damned, Robert Palmer, Status Quo, The Police, and many others.
